xt": "Created attachment 8984243\nLink to GitHub pull-request: https://github.com/mozilla/activity-stream/pull/4198", "author": "pulgasaur@mozilla.bugs", "id": 13394538, "time": "2018-06-07T19:12:57Z"}, {"text": "Commit pushed to master at https://github.com/mozilla/activity-stream\n\nhttps://github.com/mozilla/activity-stream/commit/b92c8c6068e5f9bb8b8df7d2b2bcbfe7226a752e\nfix(topsites): Share blob handling utils with top sites and cards (#4198)\n\nFix Bug 1467485 - Missing screenshots for TopSiteLink components in Nightly\nSigned-off-by: Jay Lim <6175557+imjching@users.noreply.github.com>", "author": "mozilla+bugcloser@davedash.com", "id": 13396818, "time": "2018-06-08T17:54:26Z"}, {"text": "*** Bug 1468032 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***", "author": "edilee@mozilla.com", "id": 13398184, "time": "2018-06-09T20:12:38Z"}, {"text": "*** Bug 1468034 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***", "author": "edilee@mozilla.com", "id": 13398186, "time": "2018-06-09T20:12:44Z"}, {"text": "*** Bug 1467677 has been marked as a duplicate of this bug. ***", "author": "edilee@mozilla.com", "id": 13398414, "time": "2018-06-10T07:21:17Z"}, {"text": "I'm still seeing this in latest Nightly, is it expected?", "author": "mcastelluccio@mozilla.com", "id": 13403141, "time": "2018-06-13T05:16:54Z"}, {"text": "It's still waiting on review in bug 1467858.", "author": "edilee@mozilla.com", "id": 13403158, "time": "2018-06-13T05:50:18Z"}, {"text": "https://hg.mozilla.org/mozilla-central/rev/ac40929aa54d", "author": "edilee@mozilla.com", "id": 13406631, "time": "2018-06-15T12:01:33Z"}, {"text": "This issue is no longer reproducible on the latest Nightly (62.0a1 - Build ID 20180615100050). Now each \"Top Site\" has its screenshot successfully displayed. \nVerified on Windows 10 x64, Ubuntu 16.04 x64 and Mac 10.13.", "author": "marius.coman@softvision.ro", "id": 13406862, "time": "2018-06-15T15:29:15Z"}], "id": 1467485, "priority": "P1", "mentors_detail": [], "cf_crash_si